metadata.name: WVL #1
metadata.description:
Launching live at Art Dubai on March 1st 2023. 

This is a collaborative project between 4 Emirati aritsts: Aisha Juma, Khalid Al Banna, Najat Makki and Juma Alhaj.

A curated selection of diverse artworks to celebrate the UAE's cornerstone values as represented visually by Sheikh Mohammed bin Rashid's signature 'WVL' hand gesture, an acronym for Win Victory Love. This project exemplifies MORROWâ€™s commitment to bringing more Emirati artists into the NFT space, through crypto art's most celebrated collaborative format: an algorithmically generated live mint.

Each unique 1/1 artwork contains elements from collage, digital drawing, and painting and will be available for a limited time period, starting from the first day of Art Dubai, 2023.
